## Access

| Action | Path |
|-|-|
| Edit symbol at line N | `{{ filename }}@/symbols/at-line/N` (symlink → body, preferred for edits) |
| Read symbol body by name | `Read {{ filename }}@/symbols/<Symbol>@/body.{{ ext }}` |
| Symbol callers/deps/refs | `Read {{ filename }}@/symbols/<Symbol>@/CALLERS.md` |
| LSP rename/actions | `ls {{ filename }}@/symbols/<Symbol>@/` |
| Diagnostics | `Read {{ filename }}@/DIAGNOSTICS.md` |
| Line range (escape hatch) | `cat {{ filename }}@/lines:M-N` (no prior read needed, not intercepted) |

